  754: init_per_suite(Config) ->
  755:     file:set_cwd(datadir(Config)),
  756:     ok = erl_tar:extract("ibm.tgz",[compressed]),
  757:     ok = erl_tar:extract("japanese.tgz",[compressed]),
  758:     ok = erl_tar:extract("oasis.tgz",[compressed]),
  759:     ok = erl_tar:extract("sun.tgz",[compressed]),
  760:     ok = erl_tar:extract("xmltest.tgz",[compressed]),
  761:     ok = change_mode(["ibm","japanese","oasis",
  762:                       "sun","xmltest"]),
  763:     Config.
  764: 
  765: -ifndef(dont_rm_test_dirs).
  766: end_per_suite(Config) ->
  767:     file:set_cwd(datadir(Config)),
  768:     ok = rm_files(["ibm","japanese","oasis","sun","xmltest"]),
  769:     ok.
  770: 
  771: -else.
  772: end_per_suite(Config) ->
  773:     ok.
  774: -endif.

  778:     io:format("Config:~n~p",[Config]),
  779:     {ok, _} = file:read_file_info(filename:join([privdir(Config)])),
  780:     code:add_patha(privdir(Config)),
  781:     Config.
  782: 
  783: 
  784: %% clean up after each testcase
  785: end_per_testcase(_Func,_Config) ->
  786:     ok.

 9897: %% Support Functions

 9899: 
 9900: %% Dir is a directory
 9901: rm_f_(Dir) ->
 9902:     {ok,CWD} = file:get_cwd(),
 9903:     {ok,FileList} = file:list_dir(Dir),
 9904:     file:set_cwd(filename:join([CWD,Dir])),
 9905:     rm_files(FileList),
 9906:     file:set_cwd(CWD),
 9907:     ? line ok = file:del_dir(Dir).
 9908: 
 9909: rm_files([])->
 9910:     ok;
 9911: rm_files([F|Fs]) ->
 9912:     case filelib:is_dir(F) of
 9913: 	true ->
 9914: 	    rm_f_(F);
 9915: 	_ ->
 9916: 	    ok = file:delete(F)
 9917:     end,
 9918:     rm_files(Fs).
 9919: 
 9920: -include_lib("kernel/include/file.hrl").
 9921: change_mode(Files) ->
 9922:     change_mode3(Files).
 9923: change_mode2(Dir)->
 9924:     {ok,CWD} = file:get_cwd(),
 9925:     {ok,FileList} = file:list_dir(Dir),
 9926:     file:set_cwd(filename:join([CWD,Dir])),
 9927:     change_mode3(FileList),
